OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775754356
OL,3,CMore than 160 people facing job losses
OL,4,Cas school goes into administration
OL,6,FMore than 160 staff members at a
OL,7,Fprivate school in Kent face losing
OL,8,Ftheir jobs, after the school went into
OL,9,Fadministration.
OL,11,FSt Lawrence College in Ramsgate which
OL,12,Ftakes children from 3 to 18, said
OL,13,Fdeclining pupil numbers and rising
OL,14,Foperational costs are partly to blame.
OL,16,FThe school, which was founded in 1879,
OL,17,Fdescribed it as "an incredibly sad
OL,18,Fday."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
