OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775754356
OL,3,CMore than 160 people facing job losses
OL,4,Cas school goes into administration
OL,6,FA spokesperson said it has kept around
OL,7,F40 staff - to assist Year 11 and Year
OL,8,F13 students who are due to sit GCSE,
OL,9,FBTEC and A-Level exams this summer.
OL,11,FIt says it's working to support around
OL,12,F500 pupils who will now have to find
OL,13,Falternative school places.
OL,15,FMatthew Westerby is Chair of the
OL,16,FCliftonville Hockey Club, one of many
OL,17,Fclubs that use the facilities at the
OL,18,Fschool.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775754356
OL,3,CMore than 160 people facing job losses
OL,4,Cas school goes into administration
OL,6,FThe former pupil said: "Obviously my
OL,7,Ffirst thoughts are with the pupils and
OL,8,Fthe teachers - who've lost their jobs,
OL,9,Fand the pupils who have to go and find
OL,10,Fanother school at such late notice.
OL,12,F"But from a community point of view,
OL,13,Fas Chairman of the hockey club, we
OL,14,Fdon't have anywhere to play in
OL,15,FSeptember at the moment.
OL,17,F"We have offers from other facilities,
OL,18,Fbut that's not ideal to travel out of
OL,19,Farea."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775754356
OL,3,CMore than 160 people facing job losses
OL,4,Cas school goes into administration
OL,6,FFormer pupil Harriet Westby added:
OL,7,F"the fact that pupils will be looking
OL,8,Ffor another school in such a short
OL,9,Fperiod of time is really disruptive.
OL,11,F"It's completely upsetting, and for
OL,12,Fthe parents, their stress will be
OL,13,Fthrough the roof, and for teachers as
OL,14,Fwell, trying to find jobs for
OL,15,FSeptember."
OL,17,FLucy, a local resident said: "I'm
OL,18,Ffeeling really terrible for all the
OL,19,Fparents, and the children who now no
OL,20,Flonger have anywhere to go to school.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775754356
OL,3,CMore than 160 people facing job losses
OL,4,Cas school goes into administration
OL,6,F"My other concern is what will they do
OL,7,Fwith the land.
OL,9,F"Is there going to be building -
OL,10,Fwhat's going to happen next?"
OL,12,FMP for East Thanet, Polly Billington,
OL,13,Fsaid: "I frankly think the decisions
OL,14,Fby the people who own St Lawrence
OL,15,FCollege are extraordinarily
OL,16,Firresponsible and frankly appalling.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775754356
OL,3,CMore than 160 people facing job losses
OL,4,Cas school goes into administration
OL,6,F"To leave so many hundreds of families
OL,7,Fand indeed more than 100 staff with
OL,8,Fless than a week's notice for the fact
OL,9,Fthat they're going to close the school
OL,10,Fis extraordinarily irresponsible and
OL,11,Fdemonstrates that they've put their
OL,12,Ffinancial interests ahead of the
OL,13,Feducational interests and priorities
OL,14,Fof our community, particularly the
OL,15,Fchildren who go to this school.
OL,17,F"There are children who do not have a
OL,18,Fschool place in less than a week.
OL,20,F"There are people who lost their job
OL,21,Fin less than a week.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775754356
OL,3,CMore than 160 people facing job losses
OL,4,Cas school goes into administration
OL,6,F"I will be working with Kent County
OL,7,FCouncil and with the Department for
OL,8,FEducation to ensure that these
OL,9,Fchildren can get school places because
OL,10,Fthat is the priority for these young
OL,11,Fpeople, is that they can continue
OL,12,Ftheir education.
OL,14,FGraham Carter, Chair of Governors at
OL,15,FSt Lawrence College, said: "This is an
OL,16,Fincredibly sad day for everyone
OL,17,Fconnected with St Lawrence College.
OL,26,@wD@\OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
