OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775754356
OL,3,CMore than 160 people facing job losses
OL,4,Cas school goes into administration
OL,6,F"For 146 years, this school has been
OL,7,Fat the heart of the Ramsgate
OL,8,Fcommunity, and generations of pupils
OL,9,Fhave benefitted from the dedication of
OL,10,Four staff and the strength of our
OL,11,Fcommunity.
OL,13,F"We explored every possible option to
OL,14,Fsecure the school's future, and I want
OL,15,Fto thank everyone who worked so hard
OL,16,Fto find a way forward.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775754356
OL,3,CMore than 160 people facing job losses
OL,4,Cas school goes into administration
OL,6,F"While this is not the outcome we
OL,7,Fwanted, our focus now is on supporting
OL,8,Four examination-year pupils to
OL,9,Fcomplete their studies, helping
OL,10,Ffamilies find new school places, and
OL,11,Fensuring our colleagues receive the
OL,12,Fsupport they deserve."
